{"tid":1451190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"停喇，唔好再討論點辨認鬼","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T19:51:17.000Z","uid":40663,"like":57,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b82e5e4af30c047de1ddd1af800576e09601013b","tid":1451190,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:30:01.000Z","msg":"其實教大家點去捉鬼，點整合鬼嘅特徵都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇用</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為班狗唔係傻，咁多年UC經驗，佢地一早已經有唔同嘅應對方法，做UC都有好幾百甚至幾千套標準，我地冇可能整合得晒。<br />\n<br />\n而更恐怖嘅在於，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我懷疑班狗最終目的仍然係分化</span></span>，點解咁講？當今次我地知原來前線咁多鬼，下次我地就會不斷捉鬼，每個勇武對身邊兄弟都會有懷疑，行動又點會一致。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我地依家唔係要討論點樣捉鬼，係要大家調整好心態，劉業成上任後，班狗變晒輕裝上陣，大概都係TG再冇盾衝過嚟，我地無論點都會有人落後，所以下次，懇請大家企喺度，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">set鐵馬攔晒所有地方包括行人路同草叢</span></span>，先廢速龍，迫佢用返盾陣推，唔用盾陣，就亂棍打狗。<br />\n<br />\n特別係有鬼禁低義士，請大家一齊衝返返去救人，咁先係齊上齊落，唔好再轉身走，今日太古落到底大家唔走，班狗就仆硬街架知唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n劉業成手段好勁好狠冇底線，但我地輸呢役，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就乜都冇架喇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1個人冇可能拉得晒200萬人，<br />\n但200萬人就點都救到1個人。"},{"pid":"c9e9ae5ba35788100f489e71768c47909dc7aeb6","tid":1451190,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:30:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81c85830e9e2c6795bcbad8304c4b4cb03457d37","tid":1451190,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:31:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c2edaf385e34dac519fef6aa1488d25166013af","tid":1451190,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:31:10.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"9b7a565f55c9cc1defc39b71e6e04255b5a808d3","tid":1451190,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:31:20.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"bb42c8aa944b682bbf0c366524a0751d419f773f","tid":1451190,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:31:32.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"8d3ab692d49990742771ab9dd052a9665ab389bb","tid":1451190,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:31:42.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"f5a8a9abe9e8e5eb68a881c43cab9432611145b1","tid":1451190,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:31:43.000Z","msg":"唔洗多講，幾萬人一齊還拖"},{"pid":"a731a7d13e47ddceff676e057f259a646ff2f7b4","tid":1451190,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:31:52.000Z","msg":"推, 真係要諗個方法全民參與"},{"pid":"4e49fffb6af91efacb89023f92267a23798c8236","tid":1451190,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:31:53.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"fbef4950b26335427f0eb504795f17f05dd12c7a","tid":1451190,"uid":217185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de7ec0f585493e70d5d473a40d05bc54a557aa0a","tid":1451190,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:03.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"c4d3e70a83dfaddec5ca01683d031424840f7e5d","tid":1451190,"uid":224104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:07.000Z","msg":"觀念正確<br />\n諗一個唔會有鬼既新方向可能仲快過諗點樣認鬼"},{"pid":"b5f3cd2d911e17058b4480c39ac6121ded36e0a2","tid":1451190,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:14.000Z","msg":"革"},{"pid":"321aeaecf81b8cdd2268c391c30110c708556da3","tid":1451190,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:30.000Z","msg":"命"},{"pid":"84b6a6947fd415314b499471ae5e0c0ad8bf674a","tid":1451190,"uid":75823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:43.000Z","msg":"鬼都要捉架喇，差在係真捉出黎打，定係暗中提防，唔係前線又比人帶頭？"},{"pid":"f77e9ddad21085d1ebe487a7c2074f99bd1eb46c","tid":1451190,"uid":224104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2